<br />

<br />
I'd say the epic 1.5's need alot of adjusting across all classes to make them 1) do-able by less than 5 groups of people in lower teir guilds (pre-elemental, VT) 2) More equal in usefullness at all levels of play 3) Slightly longer to complete, with more story elements and lore.  I think the encounters should be easier, and the quests made longer to compensate, personally (they are EPIC quests afterall...). 
<br />

<br />
Fix bolt spell graphics so they look like a BOLT again!
<br />

<br />
Increase exp rewards on ALL quests across the board by ALOT, questing for exp should be a viable option ESPECIALLY at low levels.  With exp zones becoming deserted more often at low levels these players need other options than simple grinding for exp.  The task system sucks, and needs to give ALOT more exp.  Long hard quests at low levels should yeild at least 1 yellow of exp (by low levels I mean 1-50).  Completing epic 1.0 should give you the amount of exp needed to FILL your bar at 51, for all classes.  I REALLY think this would make the game ALOT more fun.  And speaking of making the game alot more fun...
