				<td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">Pff, lemme see... gonna be a nice list of all kinds of tiny things i guess <img src="images/smiles/icon_smile.gif" alt="icon_smile" border="0" /> Most of the things in my list are aimed at the casual players with a bunch of friends on a server that is NOT in their timezone (i have a bunch of US friends on my server and enjoy playing with them, i just play EU time on a US server)
<br />

<br />
<ol type="1">
<br />
<li>Make a search option in bazaar that allows you to search for the spell levels. It's annoying enough to get some spells, but it's near impossible to wade through the level 10 spells for 200p that people put up.
<br />

<br />
<li>Make LDoN missions interesting XP wise. Before the XP was nerfed the missions were popular without getting everyone there (in other words, people were still playing PoP and later on GoD, no matter what LDoN did). Right now it's near impossible for me to get LDoN groups cause i play at EU times on a US based server (and i would like to complete my pet focus and upgrade my cleric with some normal equipment) <img src="images/smiles/eusa_pray.gif" alt="Pray" border="0" /> 
<br />

<br />
<li>Improve lag, pings have gone up to 400+ in the last 3 months. Pings were 200-400 in May and now are 400-1400 for EU players.
<br />

<br />
<li>give casual players another way of getting Elemental Planes access... not some simple quest, but something that challenges them as well as the raids would, i would think either a long hard quests with several single group 65+ encounters, or 3 subflags that can be done with 2 or 3 group 65 toons. Loot should not be something these raids give off, atleast, not something they should be done for...further... NEVER EVER DO THIS FOR PoTIME ! 
<br />

<br />
Eventually this would help more people enjoy GoD and OoW content at the higher end (GoD is almost empty atm cause those people wanting to explore it can't and those that can are not interested anymore....)
<br />

<br />
(this would help family guilds and people that play on a server not in their timezone)
<br />

<br />
<li>Improve framerate lag. PoK is a good point to measure and any system should be able to turn down grpahics enough to move around there. Check various graphics implementations cause currently my old system is as fast as my new system is with the same amount of models on. The new engine that came with OoW is already an improvement, although i still notice that i get a lot of lag in PoK unless i go to lowest settings (my old system runs at higher settings with less lag).
<br />

<br />
<li>In general, reduce quest camp times, make the engagements harder, but easier to get to the mob (examples are: triggered Phinny that requires 3 good level 55 groups, Quillmane triggered but a nice fight for a 55 group etc). This should also go for many of the key quests (Howlong Stones, Veeshan Peaks (already done for this i think), Vex Thal, etc).
<br />
</ol>
<br />

<br />
<ol type="1">
<br />
<li>MAGE: Remove Pearl cost from CotH, clerics don't need the money drain on Virtue line, so why should we keep shelling out cash for CotH? (sure, pdot is more expensive, but come on, clerics could make plat in PoK by just asking donations... right now donations stayed the same and clerics don't need pdots anymore... result is they make 11p more per donation as compared to before this change (i don't mind, i bot a cleric))
<br />

<br />
<li>MAGE: Revise the pet melee system. Currently giving a pet a weapon doesn't change it's damage output except for procs. Changing this to a more flexible and usable system would open up a lot of possibilities in future expansions and would also make balancing the pets easier (summoned pet toys would get more important, but also the old world stuff like Gnoll Hide Lariat could be worth a shot again, depending your needs)
<br />

<br />
<li>MAGE: improve our pet DPS so it can serve as a tank while soloing/duoing (it can handle a beating, i just need to spent too much mana on nukes to be effective (and that is with a cleric there btw)) Of course this goes together with the previous item. If that is changed, this should be easily doable (mage only rightclicks that give LORE, NO RENT, NO DROP items that are pet only (make pets wield nodrop items or make a new label "NOTRADE"))
<br />
</ol>
<br />

<br />
Think this is it for now... will think of more no doubt, so i will edit this post later on.<br />_________________<br />In the end everything is okay.
<br />
If it's not okay it's not the end.
<br />

<br />
<a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=29332">Oliadar</a>, Level 67 Erudite Arch Mage
