				<td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">-Complete everything requested on our top ten list.
<br />

<br />
-Upgrade the con-system to show greater level of detail with regards to surivability. This should allow a player to get a different color con based not just based upon the mob/player's level, but based upon whether they are in a raid, group or solo. 
<br />

<br />
-Allow Grand Masters (or with research 200) to disassemble tradeskill crafted spell scrolls and items.
<br />

<br />
-Add a /dzaddpla <name> (type) command to invite a person to join your group, just like you can send expedition invites to any player on the server.
<br />

<br />
-Create a summon aug spell set for mages. These augs will be all/all equipable and have stats only when the mage is in the group or raid. (kinda like bard songs) 
<br />

<br />
-Create a spell set which allows a Magician to summon an elemental copy of a mob, rather than relying on summoned mobs already being in a zone.  This elemental when summoned will take the shape of any MoB the mage has targeted. There will be 2 levels of this spell. Level 1 will be compareable in DPS to the current DC pets and have a perm duration. Level 2 will be compareable to the current Charmed mobs and have a random duration based upon the Mages SV to that element. (water SV cold, fire SV fire, air SV magic, earth SV to disease)   Mahahaha!<br />_________________<br /><img src="http://members.cox.net/dtresendes/danisig.png" border="0" />
